				"5A5B000DCCDD000D"
			]
			description: ["The EBF operates at 2700K. Titanium melts at 1941K; Stainless Steel and all Chrome alloys fall within this temperature range. The MV machine floor is assembled — Electrolyzer, Chemical Reactor, upgraded ore processing, full alloy and circuit production. What remains requires one more boss gate: the Twilight Lich commands the second major Twilight Forest structure and carries the Lich Trophy, which is woven into the HV Machine Hull recipe. Prepare your equipment and return to the forest."]
